reviewText: Love all the people in it, had high expectations, left disappointed. I've heard everything they shared. Was hoping for some fresh content. Misleading title too.
Amazing stories of loving, selfless people going about doing God's business just as Jesus would do.  Inspring, a must see to inspire hope for the world.
This is a passion-stirring documentary on what it looks like to live as children of God, making an impact in the world.
Excellent and Inspiring Movie. Love the real stories and has some really cool songs in it. Powerful. Makes you want to live for God!
if you're a believer this will push you and stretch your perception of who GOD is. I highly recommend it.
Powerful, powerful movie! A must see!!!
Unbelievable movie of connecting God with people to be healed
Loved it need more uplifting encouragement for the Family of God...
